---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="DecodeMyBoss - Corporate Speak Decoder" description="Paste a message from your boss. Get the real meaning, toxicity score, and action plan. Free.">
  <div class="pt-24 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
      <a href="/en/apps" class="text-sm text-text-muted hover:text-accent-purple transition-colors">&larr; All apps</a>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 mt-8 mb-12">
        <img src="/apps/decode-my-boss-icon.png" alt="DecodeMyBoss icon" width="128" height="128" class="rounded-[28px] shadow-lg" />
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-3"><span class="gradient-text">DecodeMyBoss</span></h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-text-muted">Corporate Speak Decoder</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Screenshots -->
      <div class="mb-12 overflow-x-auto">
        <div class="flex gap-4 pb-4" style="min-width: max-content;">
          <img src="/apps/decode-my-boss/screenshots/en/screenshot_1.png" alt="Decode result" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/apps/decode-my-boss/screenshots/en/screenshot_2.png" alt="Timeline" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/apps/decode-my-boss/screenshots/en/screenshot_3.png" alt="Context picker" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/apps/decode-my-boss/screenshots/en/screenshot_4.png" alt="Templates" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/apps/decode-my-boss/screenshots/en/screenshot_5.png" alt="Onboarding" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/apps/decode-my-boss/screenshots/en/screenshot_6.png" alt="Dark mode" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/apps/decode-my-boss/screenshots/en/screenshot_7.png" alt="Settings" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card-hover p-8 rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card mb-8">
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Your boss sent a message. What does it REALLY mean? "Per my last email..." "As previously discussed..." "Going forward, let's ensure alignment..." Sound familiar? Decode My Boss translates corporate speak into plain English — instantly and privately.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">How It Works</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          1. Paste the message (email, Slack, Teams — anything). 2. AI decodes the real meaning line by line. 3. Get your Toxicity Score, Red Flags, and action plan.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">What You Get</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-text-muted mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Plain English Translation</strong> — line-by-line decode of what they actually meant</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Toxicity Score</strong> — 0-100% with breakdown: passive aggression, gaslighting, micromanagement, blame shifting, guilt tripping</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Red Flags</strong> — with severity levels: low, medium, high, critical</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Playbook</strong> — concrete steps: document, escalate, talk to HR, or relax</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Share Verdict Card</strong> — share your decode with coworkers. No original message included — just the verdict</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">100% Private. Zero Servers.</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Your boss's message never leaves your iPhone. AI analysis runs entirely on-device using Apple Intelligence. No accounts. No cloud. No one will ever know. Devices without Apple Intelligence use Google Gemini only with your explicit permission. Free forever. No ads. No subscriptions. We built this because everyone deserves to understand what's really being said at work.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-hover p-8 rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Coming to App Store</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted">Decode My Boss is preparing for release. Free for iOS.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-hover p-8 rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Privacy</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-3">Text is analyzed on-device via Apple Intelligence. On devices without Apple Intelligence, Google Gemini is used only with your explicit permission. No data is stored.</p>
        <a href="/apps/decode-my-boss/privacy" class="text-sm text-accent-purple hover:underline">Privacy Policy &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <div class="text-sm text-text-muted">
        <p>Questions or feedback: <a href="mailto:magic4e@gmail.com" class="text-accent-purple hover:underline">magic4e@gmail.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
